These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, tea, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, july, june, october
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person watching satire movies and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage         | mirinda      | coffee | almond-milk | tea |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Birthday     | march     | june    | october    | july      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, analyst, coach, mechanic
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, guinea-pig, cat
1. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the coach##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the analyst##1
7. the designer is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the mechanic is between the analyst and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Job   | coach     | designer | mechanic  | analyst |
| Pet     | cat        | guinea-pig  | horse    | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, skydiving, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
House: victorian, palace, gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. the german is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
2. the argentine is the cape-cod house##1
3. the victorian house is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Hobby          | filmmaking | hiking   | rock-climbing     | skydiving     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| House     | cape-cod      | palace | gothic-revival | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
City: hannover, london, marseilles, san-francisco
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, chaman, game, siglo
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the chaman-smoker##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| City   | marseilles  | san-francisco      | hannover        | london     |
| Cigar         | game | bluemaster | siglo | chaman   |

