.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, goldfish, snake
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, scientist, freelancer, nurse
1. the japanese is the owner of the snake##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the software-developer is the owner of the snake##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the software-developer is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
9. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Pet         | hamster      | snake | cat      | goldfish |
| Job     | scientist | software-developer        | nurse       | freelancer  |

