.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kiwi, lemon, pepper
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, satire, fantasy, mystery
City: berlin, hannover, edinburgh, boston
1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lemon   | pepper      | kiwi       | apricot |
| Movie-Genre   | action | mystery | fantasy     | satire |
| City     | boston     | hannover  | berlin | edinburgh |

