.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, water-polo, sailing, volleyball
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip, sunflower, lily
1. the person who growssunflower is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who growstulip is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who growsmarigold##2
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Sport   | sailing     | water-polo | volleyball   | golf     |
| Flower           | marigold | tulip         | lily         | sunflower |

