.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, amber, black, brown
4 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, chinchilla, snake
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who likes coral##1
3. the owner of the snake is the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes black is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the owner of the rat and the person who likes coral##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
7. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes amber and the person who likes black##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Color         | amber | coral      | black       | brown    |
| Pet           | lizard  | chinchilla  | snake | rat |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

