.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different games are played: billiard, go, chess, snooker
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, amber, green
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
3. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person playing chess##1
9. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Game   | go         | billiard  | chess     | snooker         |
| Color        | green | fuchsia | light-blue | amber         |
| Sport      | rugby         | skiing  | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |

