.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, vegafina, havana, bolivar
House: tower, palace, art-deco, modern
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
 2. the tower house is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the art-deco house is between the vegafina-smoker and the blend-smoker##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is the havana-smoker##1
 7. the modern house is on the far right##1
 8. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the palace house is between the bolivar-smoker and the havana-smoker##2
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar   | blend  | havana    | vegafina | bolivar    |
| House   | tower | art-deco | palace  | modern |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse    | dog        | horse   |

