.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, scooter, train
City: colone, miami, venice, berlin
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
4. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
8. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport      | jet-ski                | train  | van | scooter   |
| City           | berlin | miami | colone   | venice |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

