.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, fanta, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, october, august
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | 7up | mirinda | fanta |
| Birthday   | october    | july     | august    | september |

