.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, r&b, metal, trance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, begonia, lily, tulip
1. the person who growsbegonia is between the person drinking fanta and the fan of classical##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
5. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
7. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
8. the fan of metal is the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the fan of trance is between the person who growslily and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | coffee  | sprite    |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | r&b | trance | classical |
| Flower           | tulip      | lily       | begonia   | iris      |

