.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
House: cape-cod, palace, victorian, modern
4 different pets are kept: fish, cat, horse, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the victorian house is in an even position##4
2. the palace house is between the modern house and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the modern house is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's sport is cycling and the owner of the fish##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| House         | cape-cod    | victorian | palace  | modern  |
| Pet   | horse | cat       | mouse | fish |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

