.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
4 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, poker, snooker
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, scooter, helicopter
1. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the bus is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person playing snooker##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person playing canasta is the person driving the bus##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Game   | snooker | canasta      | mah-jongg | poker |
| Transport           | scooter   | bus  | motorbike     | helicopter |

