The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, sports, satire, animation
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening, drawing, board-games
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person watching satire movies##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching animation movies##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Movie-Genre       | satire   | horror | sports | animation |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing      | gardening    | woodworking   |

