4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

