.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
City: paris, san-francisco, hamburg, liverpool
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, whist, canasta
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to paris##2
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
7. the person playing whist is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| City   | liverpool | san-francisco | paris | hamburg      |
| Game     | monopoly   | backgammon        | canasta   | whist       |

 